{"tid":1765634,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（唔好畀佢停）愛爾蘭戰線","createTime":"2019-12-02T04:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T04:09:17.000Z","uid":154277,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1356613a31eb7d622613eb302397d891c3c8d718","tid":1765634,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:04:34.000Z","msg":"有住在愛爾蘭的香港人及內地人接受當地報章《愛爾蘭時報》訪問，指愛爾蘭的中國社區就是監視網絡的一部份，有人是出於任務，其他人則是出於愛國愛黨而做。其中一名受訪者就因參加當地的聲援示威，被人拍照放在社交網上，而被中國僱主辭退。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳送門：</strong><br />\nChina has &lsquo;a lot of spies&rsquo; in Ireland, activists claim<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/asia-pacific/china-has-a-lot-of-spies-in-ireland-activists-claim-1.4097005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishtimes.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fchina-has-a-lot-of-spies-in-ireland-activists-claim-1.4097005&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0YCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=2d112376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/asia-pacific/china-has-a-lot-of-spies-in-ireland-activists-claim-1.4097005</a><br />\n<br />\n【居愛爾蘭港人聲援示威被解僱 憂被捕港人被關再教育營】<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191202/60330060?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR04yeEkow05cViADl2ZwPXbKbdBS6HKVMM5-PvFRRgVP69msVuxWXHjU0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191202%2F60330060%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR04yeEkow05cViADl2ZwPXbKbdBS6HKVMM5-PvFRRgVP69msVuxWXHjU0g&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0YCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=01069137\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191202%2F60330060%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia